===Owens Valley resources===

* {{cite book | author = Burton, Jeff | title = The Archeology of Somewhere: Archeological Testing Along U.S. Highway 395, Manzanar National Historic Site | publisher = Western Archeological Center, National Park Service, United States Department of the Interior | year = 1998 | id = Publications in Anthropology 72 (''Covers archeological finds at Manzanar from the pre-World War II, wartime and post-war periods'')}}
* {{cite book | author = Chalfant, William A. | title = Story Of Inyo | publisher = Chalfant Press | year = 1980 | isbn = 0-912494-34-4}}
